Description: Gibson Memphis Custom ES-335 Limited Edition 2017 Pelham Blue + OHSC and COA Lovies Guitars has up for grabs a Limited Edition ES-335 in Pelham Blue! This is a Memphis Custom with an extremely nice and dark Rosewood Fretboard! It’s still in mint condition, the setup and everything is just as it was from the factory! The 335’s are some of the most versatile guitars you could ever play! This one is exactly the same! It has an incredible color in the Pelham Blue that is sure to stand out from the rest! See many images included Weighs in at: 8.35 lbs .863″ at the 1st fret 1.004″ at the 12th fret 1.695″ Nut Width Serial: 10607740 SKU: 2012 The legendary Gibson semi-solid, now available for a limited time with Gibson’s classic Pelham Blue finish. Features include a tubeless Historic truss rod, PAF-style Burstbucker 1 & 2 pickups, redesigned neck shape for increased strength and enhanced playing comfort, top-quality hardware, and an ABR-1 Bridge with titanium bridge saddles for increased sustain, presence and clarity.
